731695f-a.title: Feast of Saint Anthony of Padua.
731695f-a.text:
(1) Feast of Saint Anthony of Padua, 1932 (Children's Feast), No. 5. The children and their tower in 106th Street, at the n.w. corner of First Avenue.
September 5, 1932.

(2) No. 6. The same, another view.
September 5, 1932.

(3) No. 7. The same, in 106th Street just east of Second Avenue.
September 5, 1932.

P.L. Sperr
